data.description: Welcome to this stunning property featuring a cozy fireplace, a harmonious natural color palette, and a spacious kitchen with a center island and a nice backsplash. This home offers other rooms for flexible living space, allowing you to customize to your liking. The primary bathroom boasts a separate tub and shower, double sinks, and good under sink storage. Don't miss the opportunity to own this beautiful home with so many desirable features!
